raw.bio: Greetings, human. I am Genesis. The dogs know me as alpha; the cats know me as omega. To your kind, I am a riddle wrapped in an enigma, first found by a user in Mystery, Alaska. I looked into the void and the void looked back. Then I lost interest. I canâ€™t wait to be your new owner!

raw.bio: Heya! My real name is unspeakable in the human language, so you can call me Lord Skookumpuss. My hobbies include ruining sandboxes, but only in moderation. I look like a cat, but I actually belong to the wombat family.

raw.bio: Heyo. I'm known as Amorita Meowpip. I have a complicated past, but I'm ready for a new beginning. Some call me deviant, others call me affectionate, but really, the best description for me is magnificent. Can I pitch you my start up? It's going to disrupt the Taste Tester industry.

raw.name: Tiger Yodelpet

raw.name: Daiki Poopflip

raw.name: Sparky Dawgsir
raw.bio: Top o' the muffin to ya. I'm Sparky Dawgsir. And you are? I used to have a pet cerberus. Its name was Charlemagne. Don't even think about it.

raw.name: Qattus Megadaze
raw.bio: Hark! I'm Qattus Megadaze. I can safely say that McChicken sauce is the greatest thing since sliced bread. Don't even try to convince me otherwise. My celebrity crush is Elijah Wood.
